---
// Misaka Network - About Page
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
        title="关于 - Misaka Network"
        description="实验日志 - 关于这个博客和它的创建者"
>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Page Header -->
        <div class="mb-12 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-glow" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
                实验日志 #10032
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-misaka-circuit font-mono">
                // EXPERIMENT_LOG: MISAKA_NETWORK
            </p>
            <div class="divider-circuit mt-6"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Left Column - Main Content -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
                <!-- About Section -->
                <section class="network-panel">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-misaka-circuit mb-6 font-mono flex items-center space-x-2">
                        <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-misaka-circuit rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
                        <span>// About This Network</span>
                    </h2>

                    <div class="prose prose-lg">
                        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
                            欢迎来到 <strong class="text-misaka-blue">Misaka Network</strong> -
                            一个专注于技术、代码与实验的数字空间。
                        </p>

                        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
                            这里记录着关于软件开发、系统架构、前端技术以及各种有趣实验的观察与思考。
                            就像学园都市的"御坂网络"一样，这里汇聚着来自不同领域的知识与经验。
                        </p>

                        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-misaka-blue pl-4 italic my-6"
                                    style="color: var(--text-muted);">
                            "不管是多么微不足道的能力，只要使用方式正确，就能发挥出惊人的威力。"
                            <footer class="text-sm mt-2">— 某科学的超电磁炮</footer>
                        </blockquote>

                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-misaka-circuit mb-3 mt-8">技术栈</h3>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
                            <li>前端：TypeScript, React, Vue, Astro</li>
                            <li>后端：Node.js, Python, Go</li>
                            <li>数据库：PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis</li>
                            <li>DevOps：Docker, Kubernetes, GitHub Actions</li>
                            <li>云平台：Cloudflare, AWS, Vercel</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-misaka-circuit mb-3 mt-8">关注领域</h3>
                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                            <div class="bg-misaka-circuit/10 border border-misaka-circuit/30 rounded-lg p-3">
                                <div class="text-misaka-circuit font-mono text-sm mb-1">Web Development</div>
                                <div class="text-xs" style="color: var(--text-muted);">现代 Web 应用开发</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-misaka-blue/10 border border-misaka-blue/30 rounded-lg p-3">
                                <div class="text-misaka-blue font-mono text-sm mb-1">Cloud Native</div>
                                <div class="text-xs" style="color: var(--text-muted);">云原生架构与部署</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-misaka-accent/10 border border-misaka-accent/30 rounded-lg p-3">
                                <div class="text-misaka-accent font-mono text-sm mb-1">Performance</div>
                                <div class="text-xs" style="color: var(--text-muted);">性能优化与监控</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-misaka-circuit/10 border border-misaka-circuit/30 rounded-lg p-3">
                                <div class="text-misaka-circuit font-mono text-sm mb-1">Open Source</div>
                                <div class="text-xs" style="color: var(--text-muted);">开源项目贡献</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Blog Philosophy -->
                <section class="network-panel">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-misaka-circuit mb-6 font-mono flex items-center space-x-2">
                        <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-misaka-blue rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
                        <span>// Writing Philosophy</span>
                    </h2>

                    <div class="space-y-4" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
                        <p>这个博客的内容遵循以下原则：</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3">
                            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-misaka-circuit flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none"
                                     stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                          d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <strong class="text-misaka-blue">实践导向</strong> -
                                    所有文章都基于实际项目经验
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-misaka-circuit flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none"
                                     stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                          d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <strong class="text-misaka-blue">深度优先</strong> -
                                    注重原理分析而非浅尝辄止
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-misaka-circuit flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none"
                                     stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                          d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <strong class="text-misaka-blue">开源精神</strong> -
                                    分享代码和解决方案
                                </div>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-misaka-circuit flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none"
                                     stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                          d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <strong class="text-misaka-blue">持续学习</strong> -
                                    记录成长与思考过程
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Column - Sidebar -->
            <div class="space-y-8">
                <!-- System Info -->
                <div class="network-panel">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-misaka-circuit mb-4 font-mono">
                        // System Info
                    </h3>
                    <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                        <div class="flex justify-between">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-muted);">Version</span>
                            <span class="text-misaka-blue font-mono">v2.0</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-muted);">Built with</span>
                            <span class="text-misaka-circuit font-mono">Astro</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-muted);">Hosted on</span>
                            <span class="text-misaka-accent font-mono">Cloudflare</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex justify-between">
                            <span style="color: var(--text-muted);">Status</span>
                            <span class="text-misaka-circuit font-mono flex items-center space-x-1">
								<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-misaka-circuit rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
								<span>Online</span>
							</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Contact -->
                <div class="network-panel">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-misaka-circuit mb-4 font-mono">
                        // Contact
                    </h3>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <a
                                href="https://github.com"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                class="flex items-center space-x-2 hover:text-misaka-blue transition-colors p-2 rounded hover:bg-misaka-circuit/10"
                                style="color: var(--text-secondary);"
                        >
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/>
                            </svg>
                            <span>GitHub</span>
                        </a>
                        <a
                                href="/rss.xml"
                                class="flex items-center space-x-2 hover:text-misaka-blue transition-colors p-2 rounded hover:bg-misaka-circuit/10"
                                style="color: var(--text-secondary);"
                        >
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
                                      d="M6 5c7.18 0 13 5.82 13 13M6 11a7 7 0 017 7m-6 0a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0z"/>
                            </svg>
                            <span>RSS 订阅</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Timeline -->
                <div class="network-panel">
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-misaka-circuit mb-4 font-mono">
                        // Timeline
                    </h3>
                    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-misaka-blue rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-medium" style="color: var(--text-primary);">2024</div>
                                <div class="text-xs" style="color: var(--text-muted);">博客重构，采用 Astro + Tailwind
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-misaka-circuit rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-medium" style="color: var(--text-primary);">2023</div>
                                <div class="text-xs" style="color: var(--text-muted);">开始技术博客写作</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
